short_description: Elegant diamond studs from the Palesa Collection
long_description: These exquisite Circle of Life Studs represent the eternal bond of love and the continuous cycle of life. Crafted in 18k yellow gold with brilliant diamonds, they embody the femininity and resilience that the Palesa Collection celebrates.

The Marquise Kiss Bracelet features a delicate chain of marquise-cut diamonds that dance around the wrist like gentle kisses. Each diamond is carefully selected and set in 18k yellow gold, creating a piece that speaks to the heart.

Inspired by the eternal bloom of African flowers, this ring features a stunning floral motif with diamonds set in 18k yellow gold. The design captures the essence of growth, beauty, and the enduring spirit of femininity.

The Heritage Pendant pays homage to traditional African jewelry while embracing contemporary elegance. Featuring a geometric pattern with diamonds set in 18k yellow gold, it connects the wearer to their roots while celebrating their journey forward.
